{"tid":2064811,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳文敏：涉及武力才算顛覆","createTime":"2020-06-15T05:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T06:13:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"96274e4128081fa72814415ef975d80025439fda","tid":2064811,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:26:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200615/3X6DVY7LWJPGX67FGY2R5TKW5E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200615%2F3X6DVY7LWJPGX67FGY2R5TKW5E%2F&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8ns01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=832bebc9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200615%2F3X6DVY7LWJPGX67FGY2R5TKW5E%2F&h=71135922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200615/3X6DVY7LWJPGX67FGY2R5TKW5E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n陳文敏：涉及武力才算顛覆<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港大法律學院公法講座教授陳文敏接受訪問時強調，港版國安法雖屬全國性法律，但應寫明香港法院有權以普通法原則審理和解釋，又指國安法屬限制人身自由刑法，針對範圍不能無限擴闊，如分裂國家、顛覆國家政權罪行必須要涉及或鼓吹武力，有實際效果才能成立。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：李家超：警秘密對付平民高手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RDSQ3VJ5INPKWGH3YVTFLPJARM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRDSQ3VJ5INPKWGH3YVTFLPJARM.jpg&h=fba39b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳文敏指國安法屬限制人身自由刑法，針對範圍不能無限擴闊。張志華攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「搖吓兩支旗未必做到」<br />\n<br />\n陳文敏接受商台訪問時強調，審議國安相關案件時，毋須設特別。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。威遊行中舉起「港獨」旗幟，他指要考慮是否真正能推翻國家政權，「搖吓兩支旗呢，係未必做到」。<br />\n<br />\n他又指政府界定「外部勢力」非常模糊，香港作為國際城巿，很多本地團體都與外國政治團體有正常交往，如香港天主教與梵蒂岡有連繫，「遲啲如果中、梵關係唔好嘅時候，呢個係咪又會變成梵蒂岡干預香港教會？」擔心不少非政治組織「都唔知幾時會踩到（紅）線」。<br />\n■記者林俊謙"},{"pid":"a21d49615c4edee6022a8320edbf42685a24c27d","tid":2064811,"uid":103842,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:29:26.000Z","msg":"d法律撚到底幾時先醒<br />\n無論你個條文點寫都好 都係中共說了算<br />\n佢一立完 你痌督尿黃d都可以話你犯法 <br />\n<br />\n係度執著個條文根本就弱撚智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea564d39e84c5a45f27b222854b2597084e1c9bb","tid":2064811,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:34:41.000Z","msg":"中共戰略好成功<br />\n推個辣到仆街嘅國安法引你班傻仔自動支持23條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9efd0d179d672242b4c9fa6d1b7315c878bf29","tid":2064811,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea564d39e84c5a45f27b222854b2597084e1c9bb","tid":2064811,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:34:41.000Z","msg":"中共戰略好成功<br />\n推個辣到仆街嘅國安法引你班傻仔自動支持23條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:36:02.000Z","msg":"中國人最愛調和的乜乜乜"},{"pid":"d852a3bf4b39b0c989a32563328986051648ea7f","tid":2064811,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:36:45.000Z","msg":"共產黨話你係顛覆就係顛覆架啦"},{"pid":"3fdf0209ce01d86d679005f2b9494c4c0b9cabcd","tid":2064811,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKwycgX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKwycgX.jpg&h=fe8116ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4111cbedb908a5bfbe55600274da35e301759e1","tid":2064811,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fdf0209ce01d86d679005f2b9494c4c0b9cabcd","tid":2064811,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"ht